references:
As the user mainly pay attention to the top items on the recommended
list, we want the top items ranked by our model with less error. In
our experiment, we optimize the NDCG over top 1 and top 5 in the ranked
list. As it shown in Table 2, the NDCG@1 achieves
a score is 0.945 (the highest possible score is 1), the NDCG@5 are
very close to The NDCG@1, and both of them achieves a relatively high
score, indicating that GotFunding can rank the grant candidates well.
